 Editor's note: If you are having trouble viewing the livestream, please click here.CAPE TOWN - Finance Minister Malusi Gigaba makes his maiden appearance before Parliament s Standing Committee on Finance.The standing committee will be briefed by the National Treasury and the South African Revenue Services (Sars) on their strategic and annual performance plans.The Committee will also deal with outstanding matters from the meeting with Sars that took place on 28 March.eNCA